headline: Waters (WAT) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Waters (WAT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +5.92% and +2.59%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
